127
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:42,819
Three days from now,

128
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:44,580
I'll bring the contract over myself.

129
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,020
Darling.

130
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:13,780
Commander.

131
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:16,660
Weren't you
discussing business just now?

132
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:19,660
Your piano playing

133
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:23,020
