134
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:26,100
I couldn't stop thinking about it.

135
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,780
Why are you wearing glasses now?

136
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:32,980
Doesn't wearing glasses

137
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:35,820
