147
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,620
Please excuse me for a moment.

148
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,099
Alright.

149
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,460
Go ahead and take care of your work.

150
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:48,520
